The Satyug Collective NAME AND CERTIFICATION MARK

The name "The Satyug Collective" and the "Official The Satyug Collective Estate" certification mark
are reserved. You may fork this blueprint and build your own city. To call your
city an "Official The Satyug Collective Estate," you must pass a free community audit
verifying compliance with the core charter:
- 100% vegetarian community
- Non-violence (ahimsa) enforced in Articles of Association
- All essential services (electricity, food, health, education) provided free to shareholders
- Community-owned infrastructure (no external landlord model)
- Open-source blueprint published and maintained

Contact: open@Satyugnagari.org (proposed)

---

This project was created to demonstrate that self-sufficient, community-owned,
ethical cities are possible. Fork it. Build it. Make it better.
Live and let live.
